# рҹ“ҳ MedAssist AI вҖ“ Enterprise Healthcare Intelligence Platform

## рҹҸҘ Overview

**MedAssist AI** is an AI-powered healthcare intelligence platform built using **Python, Streamlit, Machine Learning, OCR, RAG (Retrieval-Augmented Generation), and Role-Based Authentication**.

The platform helps patients, doctors, and administrators manage healthcare workflows using intelligent automation, disease prediction, AI medical assistance, report analysis, appointment systems, and enterprise dashboards.

This project demonstrates:
- AI integration
- Healthcare workflow automation
- Machine learning deployment
- Secure authentication systems
- Enterprise dashboard architecture
- Modern SaaS UI development

